comments.text:
This bug also happens on WinXP SP3. When ever I start FireFox normally or using Control-N, I get the error.

I reported the bug a few months ago and have not seen any change, which I now understand because no one has been assigned to fix it. Really honestly I use FF all the time because of the tools I need as a web developer, but for 'normal' surfing I now use Chrome because of this bug.
